{"tid":198573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華文傳媒柒到喊！支那外交部：聯合航空拖走的是「越南裔美國公民」","createTime":"2017-04-12T15:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T05:48:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9f97b87fdb49772cd9f8ed5be5c379dc72352398","tid":198573,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1324840-20170412.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1324840-20170412.htm&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6rIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=8d85bfce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1324840-20170412.htm&h=ac46f92d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1324840-20170412.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n支那外交部指聯合航空客機事件受傷害者為<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">越南裔美國公民</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2017-04-12 HKT 16:46<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部表示，據初步了解，被人拖出聯合航空客機的受傷害者，是<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">越南裔美國公民</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n發言人陸慷在記者會被問到，被拖走的乘客是否中國人，他作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n陸慷表示，外交部關注到這宗美國國內的不幸事件，注意到事件引發美國國內外高度關切，中方希望事件能够妥善解決。"},{"pid":"fcd9ecf353acff3f02bbc188f43596ea6dbfe0c9","tid":198573,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:13:49.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢 #ChineseLivesMatters<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"907a28c823b3a5f4b5071f7554f65a8a04e1c94b","tid":198573,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T15:14:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3a95a2b1dde632fc3635e7bb9c7df5e716a8ea","tid":198573,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep